<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Thwick of Tunare</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-07 15:41:06</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The trick with waiting for Frostbite to return and giving him a second shirt has been nerfed. What happens now is, if Basil is still alive, Frostbite returns to his pen and then immediately takes off again. Thanks to Teirza and friends for trying this out.<BR>
<BR>
Paglan is still appearing, last saw him on Sunday 3/5.<BR>
<BR>
Be aware that Frostbite runs through the HG camp (and Chief Goonda's camp as well) sometimes.<BR>
<BR>
My opinion on the nerf is that it really wasn't necessary, it's hard enough to get Basil to spawn and stay alive. But I generally agree with the attempts to remove exploits from the game.<BR>
<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
